[11/06/2017 02:04:28] <font color="#ffffff">¡Tae-ju!</font>
[11/06/2017 02:05:02] <font color="#ffffff">¡Puta!</font>
[11/06/2017 02:05:03] <font color="#ffffff">Ya la tenemos armada.</font>
